headline.main: Johnson Wins in Mexico to Cement World Number One Ranking
headline.print_headline: Johnson Wins in Mexico to Cement World Number One Ranking

lead_paragraph: Dustin Johnson started his reign as world number one in the best possible way by winning the WGC-Mexico Championship in Mexico City on Sunday.
